reviews.review_text:
A great show! I was there for this one and Phil was turned all the way up from the get go.  It was his show, but EVERYBODY was hot this night.

One of the most highly underrated shows of the '83 tour.  Thanks for putting this one up.  I had a cassette copy of this same mix that has been worn down to a frazzle from overuse.
This was a great show alright one of many in a very hot year!
